"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1930196-Jessica-Pegula-Net-Worth-Olympics-Gold-Medal-Money\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  WhileJessica Pegulais one of the world's richest tennis stars, she will only earn a meagre amount for grasping gold atthe Olympicsthis summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old is representingTeam USAat this year'sParisian Games,with hopes of achieving a first-place podium finish alongside fellow starCoco Gauffin the women's doubles.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Pegula will have had her sights set on being a high achiever in the single's game, she was ultimately knocked out of the contest byEvina Svitolinain the second round.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pegula made light work ofViktorija Golubicin her opener on Sunday, winning 6-3, 6-4.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ukrainian Svitolina would prove too hot to handle in the next game, besting Pegula 4-6, 6-1, 6-3.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.985792547234877, \"rank\": 0.012933886410397083, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The talent hopes to have more success on the shared clay courts in Paris this summer, teaming up with2023 US Openwinner Gauff to compete forOlympicglory.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999971914804, \"rank\": 2.8085379609820227e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pegula is the heiress to a \\u00a35.3billion fortune thanks to her father - Terry Pegula - who owns the Buffalo Bills NFL franchise.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Terry_Pegula\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Terry Pegula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Terry_Pegula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Terry_Pegula\"}, {\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buffalo_Bills\", \"score\": 0.9999999873243725, \"rank\": 1.0650522721027589e-08, \"text\": \"Buffalo Bills\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buffalo_Bills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buffalo_Bills\"}, {\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9981743143120616, \"rank\": 0.000825985981967269, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she has earned more than \\u00a39million in prize money in her own career, she's set to inherit a whopping fortune from her 73-year-old dad.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff and Pegula were off to a flying start in the doubles at the Olympics this year, beating Australian duo Daria Saville and Ellen Perez 6-3, 6-1 in their opener on Saturday.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999992629412179, \"rank\": 5.377796511148964e-07, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daria Saville\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Saville\"}, {\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellen Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Perez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they will face stiff competition from Czech athletes Linda Noskova and Karolina Muchova on the courts on Wednesday in the second round.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9998608579426596, \"rank\": 0.00013898325249522288, \"text\": \"Czech\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.720081346443899, \"rank\": 0.22067258104243762, \"text\": \"Linda\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McMahon\"}, {\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karol\\u00edna_Muchov\\u00e1\", \"score\": 0.9999999954288796, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karolina Muchova\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karol\\u00edna_Muchov\\u00e1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karol\\u00edna_Muchov\\u00e1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If successful in her endeavours, it is reported that theU.S.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic and Paralympic Committeewill pay her \\u00a329,000 ($37,500) for winning gold at this year's games - a drop in the ocean compared to what she is set to inherit in the future.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside Bethanie Mattek-Sands, Pegula clinched a fifth-place finish at the2021 Games in Tokyo, Japan, after being knocked out by Brazilians Laura Pigossi and Luisa Stefani in the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1672, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethanie_Mattek-Sands\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bethanie Mattek-Sands\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethanie_Mattek-Sands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethanie_Mattek-Sands\"}, {\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9992834086849665, \"rank\": 0.0007159735358461384, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9583861322840128, \"rank\": 0.023181353893733943, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6220640677066592, \"rank\": 0.6075514433020808, \"text\": \"Brazilians\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbped